ABOUT


This pre-owned, Omega Seamaster Aqua Terra 231.20.39.21.06.004 is in like new condition. The watch comes as a full set (undated warranty card) and comes with additional 1 year warranty from us




All of our watches undergo a thorough inspection of accuracy, functionality and condition to meet our strict standards. Additionally, we check each watch against records to ensure authenticity and ownership status.




This rare Aqua Terra is fitted with a beautiful grey dial that is patterned with Teak Concept horizontal lines and equipped with a quick change date window. Added to which are a set of hands and indices in 18K yellow gold. This 18K yellow gold spreads throughout the smooth plain bezel and crown, that are fixed to a 38.5mm stainless steel casebody and bracelet. All of which is powered by the Omega Co-Axial Calibre 8500 automatic movement which can be seen through the exhibition caseback.




Model wears watch on 7 ¼” wrist
